Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.38,0:00:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew you'd be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.48,0:00:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd expect no less from\Nthe Anbu Black Ops...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.10,0:00:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,under the direct command\Nof the Hokage.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.95,0:00:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,To think I wouldn't be able\Nto deceive you with that corpse...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.95,0:00:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Now tell us everything.\NWhat's this about?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.83,0:02:34.50,Title,,0,0,0,,{\i1\pos(725,637)}Bonds\N\N\N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.39,0:02:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You jerk!\NWhy did you betray us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.98,0:02:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't make too much\Nof a commotion here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.36,0:02:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Things will get troublesome,\Nyou see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.07,0:02:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,- You jerk!\N- Naruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.12,0:03:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Here...take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.25,0:03:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's yours, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.59,0:03:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.55,0:03:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It was an order\Nfrom Danzo, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.35,0:03:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Danzo has teamed up\Nwith Orochimaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.33,0:03:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and is attempting\Nto do something...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.35,0:03:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You were chosen\Nto be the go-between...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.18,0:03:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,for Danzo and Orochimaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.15,0:03:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What're they planning...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.12,0:03:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,With Orochimaru, he's planning to...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.25,0:03:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,once again destroy the Leaf Village...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.25,0:03:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.19,0:04:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's not--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.47,0:04:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I can tell right away that\Nyour smile is a lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.38,0:04:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,And I can tell right away that\Nwhat you're saying is a lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.57,0:04:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that you have found me...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.74,0:05:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,my mission is considered\Na failure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.12,0:05:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't handle all of\Nyou guys by myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.54,0:05:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And...if you know that much...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.04,0:05:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,then there's no point\Nin hiding anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.46,0:05:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You're exactly right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.47,0:05:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to crush\Nthe current Leaf Village.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.83,0:05:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Say what...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.22,0:05:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The real mission I was given was\Nto gain the favor of Orochimaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.88,0:05:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and create an opportunity for\Na collaboration...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.92,0:05:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,in order to crush the Leaf Village.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.98,0:05:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know\Nwhat you're saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.65,0:05:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,- To do such a thing--\N- That's not all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.58,0:05:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I also have the duty\Nof secretly sending...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.41,0:05:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,information about Orochimaru\Nto Lord Danzo...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.62,0:05:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, I have also been\Nentrusted with a mission as a spy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.80,0:05:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep going.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.38,0:06:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Own up to everything\Nyou're hiding.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.51,0:06:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So basically what\Nyou're saying is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.76,0:06:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,while proposing the collaboration\Nwith Orochimaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.34,0:06:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,you're trying to outflank him?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.35,0:06:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been given such\Na dangerous mission...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.11,0:06:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Orochimaru will definitely betray us...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.23,0:06:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,once the Leaf Village\Nhas been crushed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.49,0:06:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's to make sure we've always\Ngot the advantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.16,0:06:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I get it...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.25,0:06:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Danzo wants to make\Nthe Leaf Village his own, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.54,0:06:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You made preparations\Nfor that all by yourself...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.14,0:06:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The information I wrote\Nin black ink
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.55,0:06:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,transforms into small animals...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.81,0:06:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,and carries the information out\Nwhile protecting itself, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.77,0:07:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,This ability of mine\Nwas valued highly...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.43,0:07:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,and so I was selected\Nfor this mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.47,0:07:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Many people will die, once again...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.98,0:07:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,if things become turbulent\Nin the Leaf Village!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.75,0:07:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you even know why\Nyou're doing this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.51,0:07:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,No idea...\NThey're my orders, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.55,0:07:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Sai, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.04,0:07:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me tell you\None more thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.43,0:07:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Sai is the name I was given\Njust for this mission...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.90,0:07:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm nobody.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.98,0:07:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a tool for Lord Danzo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.78,0:07:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.24,0:07:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,So no matter what you say\Nto me, it's pointless.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.05,0:08:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.93,0:08:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.26,0:08:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,do you hold on to\Nthat picture book with such care?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.13,0:08:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The two kids on the cover...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.01,0:08:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,are you and\Nyour older brother, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.22,0:08:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You're holding on to\Nthat picture book with such care...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.41,0:08:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,because it's the only thing\Nthat proves your existence, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.94,0:09:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't been able to discard\Nyour emotions as completely as you say.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.03,0:09:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Even Shinobi can't completely\Ndiscard their emotions.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.37,0:09:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,As proof of that...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.90,0:09:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,when I handed\Nthe picture book to you earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.00,0:09:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You said thanks and took it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.83,0:09:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You were relieved to get back...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.29,0:09:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,the picture book that can prove\Nyour existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.47,0:09:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Why does having this picture book\Nprove my own existence?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.93,0:09:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason why you don't want\Nto part with that book...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.25,0:09:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,is that you can't forsake yourself\Nas a younger brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.15,0:09:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know why?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.99,0:09:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because your bonds with\Nyour older brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.82,0:09:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,were that important to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.41,0:10:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't want to erase the bonds\Nyou have with your older brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.51,0:10:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Bonds...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.89,0:10:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but we had a look\Ninside the picture book.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.27,0:10:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Only the picture in\Nthe center-facing pages is unfinished.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.36,0:10:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Sai... I also know that you're\Nfrom The Foundation.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.28,0:10:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And I also know that\Nyou received special training...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.28,0:10:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,from Danzo in order\Nto suppress your emotions.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.41,0:10:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Special training...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.79,0:10:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the same as the evil practice...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.83,0:10:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,once conducted in the Village Hidden\Nin the Mist a.k.a. Blood Mist Village,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.71,0:10:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,in order to take away emotions.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.97,0:10:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The Blood Mist Village ...\NThe Hidden Mist...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.76,0:11:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That's where Zabuza's from!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.73,0:11:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.94,0:11:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A long time ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.94,0:11:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}in the Village Hidden in the Mist\N{\i1}a.k.a. Blood Mist Village,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.65,0:11:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}there was an extremely difficult obstacle\N{\i1}in order to become Ninja.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.62,0:11:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You even know about\N{\i1}that graduation exam...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.04,0:11:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That graduation exam?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.25,0:11:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's that graduation exam?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.01,0:11:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Fellow students kill each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.97,0:11:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Fellow comrades who all ate\N{\i1}from the same bowl...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.14,0:11:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}make teams of two\N{\i1}and fight each other...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.68,0:11:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}until one of them dies.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.17,0:11:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Comrades who until that point\N{\i1}would help each other,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.90,0:11:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}talk about their dreams\N{\i1}and compete with each other...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.64,0:12:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Looking at the flow\Nof the picture book,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.59,0:12:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,it appears you're\Ndefeating enemies...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.77,0:12:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,and taking away\Ntheir weapons and armor...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.74,0:12:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,On the facing pages at the center...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.27,0:12:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,you will end up fighting\Nyour older brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.63,0:12:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You killed your older brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.08,0:12:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.59,0:13:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I was planning on\Ngiving this to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.64,0:13:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,But when I was just about finished\Nwith the picture book, he...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.06,0:13:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,He...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.36,0:13:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,died from sickness.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.11,0:13:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean...you don't feel\Nanything or have any emotions?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.78,0:13:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean just what I said.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.33,0:13:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Even so...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.75,0:13:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,If you have a brother,\Nyou should be able to imagine...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.96,0:13:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,what it would be like\Nto lose him, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.11,0:13:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, well...you could say that...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.68,0:13:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,My brother's dead, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.80,0:13:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Then all the more...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.34,0:13:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if I should've\Nlooked like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.52,0:13:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What're you trying to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.28,0:14:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... I didn't know what kind\Nof look to make
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.48,0:14:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,when my brother died...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.29,0:14:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,In The Foundation, there were\Nmany children of broken families...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.54,0:14:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,brought about by battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.59,0:14:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,He was one of those children.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.00,0:14:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I became close with him,\Nlike a brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.77,0:14:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,We weren't related by blood...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.64,0:14:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But he often said nice things\Nabout my drawings.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.24,0:14:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,In this picture book...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.23,0:14:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,what I wanted to show him\Nmost of all...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.86,0:14:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,was what were supposed to be the final\Npictures on the facing pages.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.29,0:14:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,But after he died...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.66,0:14:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't remember\Nwhat I was going to draw.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.85,0:15:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately Sai...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.35,0:16:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be having my clone\Nstand guard over you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.32,0:16:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.45,0:16:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Now it's back to square one...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.58,0:16:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to save Sasuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.67,0:16:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't bother.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.84,0:16:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.30,0:16:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,met Sasuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.69,0:16:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasuke always has Orochimaru\Nwith him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.49,0:16:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That is to say, you'll have to fight\NOrochimaru once again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.92,0:17:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll end up being\Nchopped up into pieces...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.75,0:17:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,and turned into a test subject\Nif you pursue reckssly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.76,0:17:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.84,0:17:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.06,0:17:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasuke said he doesn't care\Nabout you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.40,0:17:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakura said you think of Sasuke like\Na brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.82,0:17:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.13,0:17:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,For a guy like that, why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.56,0:18:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you trying\Nto get him back...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.60,0:18:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,going so far as to oppose\NOrochimaru and put your life at risk?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.27,0:18:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is that?\NWhen nobody's ordering you to do so?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.70,0:18:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I used to really hate Sasuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.17,0:18:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though, like me,\Nhe didn't have a family...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.72,0:18:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,he was elite and\NI was always at the bottom.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.68,0:18:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,But it was actually fun\Nbeing with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.89,0:18:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,He...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.40,0:18:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,He's the person\Nwho acknowledged me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.02,0:18:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,more than anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.12,0:19:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.96,0:19:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,is my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.58,0:19:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a special bond\NI was finally able to make.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.97,0:19:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,A bond.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.30,0:19:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Even so...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.60,0:19:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Even so, with Orochimaru\Nas your opponent...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.93,0:19:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter\Nwho the opponent is!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.81,0:19:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,If my arms get torn off,\NI'll kick him down.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.82,0:19:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,If my legs get torn off,\NI'll bite him down.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.82,0:19:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,If my head gets torn off,\NI'll stare him down.
